room_title: Escape room "Phantom Treasures" by WeXcape in Wichita
review: I've done several escape rooms in the Wichita area and would put this toward the top of the list. We did their Phantom Treasures room and enjoyed it.

room_title: Escape room "Phantom Treasures" by WeXcape in Wichita
review: Had such a great time. My 12-year-old daughter and I did the Phantom Treasures. Such a unique experience, compared to other rooms we have been to. Our Game Master Dean was top notch and made our experience even better. Well worth it.
